Kąciki  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Kurzętnik, within Nowe Miasto County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  west of Kurzętnik,  south-west of Nowe Miasto Lubawskie, and  south-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
